Package: spl-source
Architecture: all
Depends: module-assistant, debhelper (>= 7), make, bzip2
Description: source for the spl driver.
 This package provides the source code for the spl kernel modules.
 The spl package is also required in order to make use of these
 modules. Kernel source or headers are required to compile these modules.
